webpackJsonp([59811000100659],{8582:function(e,i){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Living in Europe: Czechia or Czech Republic?",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-living-in-europe-czechia-or-czech-republic/",tags:"Y2004"},html:'<p><a title="Maybe they need a symbol, like Prince used to have" href="http://www.livingineurope.net/archives/000253.html">Living in Europe: Czechia or Czech Republic?</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"I'm now a Medienkritiker",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"DSL is female",date:"13 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-13-dsl-is-female/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"I'm now a Medienkritiker",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker/",tags:"Y2004"},html:'<p>Well, not really. But <a title="Davids Medienkritik" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/">Davids Medienkritik</a> did just post a <a title="Davids Medienkritik: We Need Your Help!" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/2004/05/we_need_your_he.html">plea to help translate</a> posts into English, and I\'ll be helping out now and again (once a week or so). </p>\n<p>Why, espcially considering that David\'s views are, um, somewhat to the right of mine? Because it\'s a good blog, and it starts good conversations. Even if Germans and Americans tend to disagree, at Medienkritik they\'re at least talking to one another. As a bilingual expat, one thing I can offer to the community is to translate things that are interesting, and David\'s points are always interesting and worth considering. </p>\n<p>Translation is hard work and I am by no means a profressional translator, but at least the <a title="Davids Medienkritik: Bush\'s Down ... Oops, He\'s Up! / Bush sinkt ... Hoppla, er steigt!" href="http://medienkritik.typepad.com/blog/2004/05/bushs_down_oops.html">first post</a> was fun. I felt like I was behind enemy lines, writing headlines for the <em>Bild-Zeiting</em>.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Phil Ringnalda",date:"11 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-11-phil-ringnalda/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Living in Europe: Czechia or Czech Republic?",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-living-in-europe-czechia-or-czech-republic/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Phil Ringnalda",date:"11 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-11-phil-ringnalda/",tags:"Y2004"},html:'<p><a title="Killer app! Killer app!" href="http://philringnalda.com/blog/2004/05/bloglines_worms_its_way_into_mozilla.php">Bloglines extension for Mozilla</a></p>'},next:{fields:{title:"",date:"11 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-11-muessen-nur-wollen/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"I'm now a Medienkritiker",date:"12 May 2004",slug:"/2004-05-12-im-now-a-medienkritiker/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:488,pageCount:1101}}}});
